0","tid":242161,"uid":116376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>壓力大</blockquote><br />\n咩事"},{"pid":"bace2b13c82b2496e3cc853cb32816abc416a855","tid":242161,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:24:05.000Z","msg":"睇緊波，但唔投入...因尋日 打算delete電腦快勞.... 点知有ex嘅iphone backup 相簿.... 仲有成千張相..... 睇完兩日都冇曬心機... 利申.....已分開就快兩年"},{"pid":"3fbadbd264b9d6bd038f24ac5edf5de61207711c","tid":242161,"uid":116376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇緊波，但唔投入...因尋日 打算delete電腦快勞.... 点知有ex嘅iphone backup 相簿.... 仲有成千張相..... 睇完兩日都冇曬心機... 利申.....已分開就快兩年</blockquote><br />\n我明 分開左三年有時時都會好掛住個ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128ada4e949e94ef0ad35b9b009c42c1b63ec523","tid":242161,"uid":82940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:26:10.000Z","msg":"叫"},{"pid":"0485e03986e763fff871649188bee2b612d5e258","tid":242161,"uid":64034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇緊波，但唔投入...因尋日 打算delete電腦快勞.... 点知有ex嘅iphone backup 相簿.... 仲有成千張相..... 睇完兩日都冇曬心機... 利申.....已分開就快兩年</blockquote><br />\n我明 分開左三年有時時都會好掛住個ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我真係冇特别 掛住佢.... 因她離開的時候把所有我們的東西delete了... between 個 app .... 所以我冇乜嘢留底... 一齊過三年.... 噚日喺電腦搵到佢個相簿.... feeling sad ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43081f847727c5bb30333f68c2d98a8d5931b89","tid":242161,"uid":46974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"分手半個月<br />\n啱啱手賤，又開返cool bo個日啲對話黎睇<br />\n見到佢用字咁絕，「就算我而一下同返你一齊，我都會因為鐘意咗第二個而同你分手」<br />\n又變得好撚灰，loop黎loop去"},{"pid":"aaacb1447a70e5f50c322c000667e96e24097384","tid":242161,"uid":116376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T17:38:36.000Z","